# Cloudflare Pages Redirects & Reverse Proxy Configuration
# Redirect api, websocket, and static resource paths to the Render backend service instance dynamically

/api/*     https://chatworld-backend.onrender.com/api/:splat     200
/ws/*      wss://chatworld-backend.onrender.com/ws/:splat       200
/static/*  https://chatworld-backend.onrender.com/static/:splat  200

# Serve SPA index.html for all other routing requests (React Router handles them)
/*         /index.html   200
